OL,3,CTwo care homes announce sudden plans
OL,4,Cto close due to soaring costs
OL,6,FResidents at two care homes in
OL,7,FSomerset have been told they will have
OL,8,Fto find alternative accommodation
OL,9,Fafter both sites announced they will
OL,10,Fclosed due to rising costs.
OL,12,FSunnymeade in Chard and Critchill
OL,13,FCourt in Frome are both run by
OL,14,FSomerset Care, which has announced
OL,15,Fplans to shut them down.
OL,17,FIt says it informed those living there
OL,18,Fof the plans on Wednesday 28 February
OL,19,Fand has now launched a consultation
OL,20,Fabout whether redundancies can be
OL,21,Fprevented for staff.
