OL,3,CTwo care homes announce sudden plans
OL,4,Cto close due to soaring costs
OL,6,FSunnymeade provides residents with
OL,7,Faround the clock care, including
OL,8,Fdementia care, while Critchill Court
OL,9,Fis a purpose-built residential home,
OL,10,Fwith 46 residents.
OL,12,FThe site in Chard also provides
OL,13,Fspecialist care and has previously
OL,14,Fbeen awarded the Gold Standards
OL,15,FFramework for the support they provide
OL,16,Fto people nearing the end of their
OL,17,Flife.
OL,19,FBoth properties are currently being
OL,20,Floaned from Somerset Council by the
OL,21,Fnon-profit.
