OL,3,CTwo care homes announce sudden plans
OL,4,Cto close due to soaring costs
OL,6,FIn a statement, a spokesperson for
OL,7,FSomerset Care said: "Critchill Court
OL,8,Fand Sunnymeade were built to meet the
OL,9,Fcare requirements and living standards
OL,10,Fof the 1970-1980s, and are regrettably
OL,11,Funable to keep pace with the
OL,12,Fincreasingly complex care requirements
OL,13,Fof 2024 and beyond.
