OL,3,CTwo care homes announce sudden plans
OL,4,Cto close due to soaring costs
OL,6,F"The sad truth is that their dated and
OL,7,Frestrictive layouts, high running
OL,8,Fcosts, repair and maintenance
OL,9,Frequirements mean that they are no
OL,10,Flonger financially viable,
OL,11,Fenvironmentally sustainable or fit to
OL,12,Fsafely meet the care needs of the
OL,13,Ffuture."
OL,15,FThe company added that it is "not
OL,16,Fimmune to the financial challenges
OL,17,Ffaced by the wider care sector".
