OL,6,FThey added: "We are truly sorry that
OL,7,Fwe have been left with no alternative
OL,8,Fbut to propose the closure of these
OL,9,Fcare homes.
OL,11,F"We have secured the assistance of the
OL,12,FSomerset Council Adult Social Care
OL,13,FTeam to independently assess the care
OL,14,Fneeds of all residents at these homes.
OL,15,FWe will gladly support individuals to
OL,16,Ftransition and settle into their new
OL,17,Fhome."
